\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2264175e2a581608f478aab455578251e80e7402","tid":141044,"uid":23103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:53:54.000Z","msg":"我今日晏就都係咁...唔知咩事<br />\n就係成個人突然好唔開心 但又唔係好知自己咩事唔開心<br />\n唔只一兩次 係間唔中就會突然發生<br />\n至少應該一個月有幾日都係咁<br />\n仲要邊做野 邊唔開心 有想喊既衝動<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d115ca14eded1dd3ce439520154e122a6f097a5b","tid":141044,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我今日晏就都係咁...唔知咩事<br />\n就係成個人突然好唔開心 但又唔係好知自己咩事唔開心<br />\n唔只一兩次 係間唔中就會突然發生<br />\n至少應該一個月有幾日都係咁<br />\n仲要邊做野 邊唔開心 有想喊既衝動<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能M到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然我都係"},{"pid":"bf21699d6254081beec641d8f960d8e45eb65b84","tid":141044,"uid":21672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:59:58.000Z","msg":"成日都係咁<br />\n不過而家幾開心安慰你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c106d9cd4b1da31c0676024d690195e6da640b49","tid":141044,"uid":52448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:08:21.000Z","msg":"每次會維持幾耐? 心情會點樣好返?"},{"pid":"ed1acc918fd6acf8084cc93bee76ea1420886bb5","tid":141044,"uid":52512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:29:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會無啦啦個人好消極唔想講嘢唔想應whatsapp...<br />\n有時可能一大堆人果陣好開心好似平時咁，一變返一個人或者對住屋企人就一句嘢都唔想講，唔係唔想理佢地，而係覺得個人好攰唔想開口同人交流，直接選擇做其他嘢唯獨係唔傾計<br />\n其實我成日會驚自己唔知有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一大堆人之後個反差更加大<img src